skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: make me work out
des:
If you're dreading working out, get 25+ motivational quotes from fitness Youtubers (including Chloe Ting, Blogilates, Whitney Simmons, MadFit) and training gurus (The Rock) who have some words of choice for you! Get inspired! We all need some motivation sometimes.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Make Me Work Out" or "Alexa, make me work out".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"

Have any feedback, comments or questions? Reach out on this Google Form! https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aCQk8eaEYT82fxZHKnhSqOvVSmxWvYWFJM7ToKXRUmY/edit?usp=sharing
